rating_comment: The host Nazmul was very friendly from the start to the end, understood the demands of the guests and provided accordingly, the place has been surprisingly attractive and peaceful which is unlikely to find inside a busy city like Dhaka. The time we spent there was magnificent, from the giant-screen movie experience to the sky-gazing in the private, rooftop patio. It's worth the money, friendly environment and zero concern - creating the best experience one could ever imagine. I'd definitely come back real soon and give the host a 5/5 for his place and hosting capabilities.
